divs: Sighting DetailsThis event was witnessed and reported by many, including local tv channel 8. Sighting ocurred during evening rush hour traffic, near sunset. This UFO was, in fact, the US Navy Seal Jumpfrogs skydiving team, doing training jumps over North Island. This was reported by local paper, led to Navy posting training schedule, and was followed up by training jumps the following Friday. I heard the hoopla, and went to see it, as scheduled, two days later.
